desctiption: Composite component. Includes Label, Search, Tree, Button
usage: The TenantFilter component is designed to filter data by tenants. `runtime.trigger('interface.tenant-filter.toggle', params)` - call from NWC codes. `runtime.app.features.tenantFilter.openTenantFilter(params)` - call from plugins. `params: {treeData, defaultCheckedKeys, handler}`
